citations:
    citation-twoiaf-nymeria:
        source: source-twoiaf
        properties:
            locator: "Ancient History: Ten Thousand Ships"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Princess Nymeria of Ny Sar: led the Rhoynar exodus after Garin the Great's defeat. Ten thousand ships, wandering to Sothoryos, Naath, Summer Isles. Union with Mors Martell. Burned the ships on arriving in Dorne. Ruled Dorne for 27 years, survived three marriages and twelve assassination attempts."
